\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The SA College of Applied Psychology is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training and is accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC. The institution has also applied for a Bachelor of Applied Social Science \'28Contact\'29 and a Postgraduate Diploma in Applied Psychology in Counselling or Coaching \'28Contact and Distance\'29. \cell \pard 

\intbl \row \pard 
\line \par\pard\trowd\trqc \trpaddl113\trpaddt113\trpaddb113\trpaddr113\trpaddfl3\trpaddft3\trpaddfb3\trpaddfr3\trgaph100\trrh100\trleft36
